    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Included with this DLC:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Cyberpunk Skin for <strong>Samurai</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/312290/extras/776244a277152ea64cfb530b624c36f5.poster.avif?t=1731506426\" width=192 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/312290/extras/776244a277152ea64cfb530b624c36f5.webm?t=1731506426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Samurai</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Samurai is a highly mobile cyborg melee assassin, capable of swiftly decimating enemies and vanishing without a trace. With mastery over swords and shurikens, and devastating multistrikes, this lethal warrior leaves a trail of cold bodies with ease.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Playstyle</strong>: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Samurai offers high-octane, swift close-range combat, featuring powerful dashes, multistrikes, and area-of-effect damage. For more precise attacks, he can unleash shurikens or kunais, making expert use of a versatile arsenal of traditional weapons, ensuring no opponent leaves unscathed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Recommended for:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players who enjoy mobile, fast-paced, and explosive gameplay.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Those willing to sacrifice defenses for extra damage to deliver swift, lethal strikes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Anyone who relishes the thrill of obliterating opponents before they can blink.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>The warrior’s path awaits.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
